rq

``bind 'set disable-completion on'`` pour désactiver la completion,  ``bind ... off`` pour la réactiver

Use xinput -- list to find out your mouse devices and disable it:
$ xinput --list | grep -Ei "mouse|touchpad" | grep -o "id=[0-9]*" | grep -o "[0-9]*" | xargs -IDEV xinput --disable DEV
